    "Html": "Hello,<br>\r\n<br>\r\nhow can I set a RibbonButton enabled/disabled depending on selected text in a RTFBox? When some text is selected, the button should be enabled, otherwise disabled.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRegards<br>\r\nCarsten\r\n",
