    "Id": "143738",
    "ThreadId": "43241",
    "Html": "Hi Carsten,<br>\r\n<br>\r\nYou should add a CanExecute handler to your CommandBinding.  In the event handler you can set the CanExecute property of the event args, depending on the text selected in your RTFBox.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlex\r\n",
    "PostedDate": "2008-12-31T10:27:22.333-08:00",
